milestones.description: Ian Billcliff and Geoff Barnett's 177-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 89 between John Davison and Ashish Bagai
Ashraful and Shakib's 116-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 109 between Aminul Islam and Khaled Mahmud
Shakib's 134 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for BAN), surpassing Nafees's 123
Ashish Bagai has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for CAN, going past Ashish Bagai's 3
This is the highest match aggregate (543) involving teams Canada & Bangladesh in ODIs
Ian Billcliff and Geoff Barnett's 177-run partnership is CAN's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 106 between Ashish Bagai and John Davison

stories.title: Saqibul seals the series for Bangladesh
stories.subTitle: Canada v Bangladesh, ICC Tri-Series, St Johns
stories.summary: Bangladesh gained vengeance over Canada, the side who beat them so famously in the 2003 World Cup ... but only just, as Ian Billcliff and Geoff Barnett led a valiant pursuit of a stiff target of 279
